  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:502px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Location_map_Known_world.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"The known world and the location of Leviathan Sound\"><img alt=\"The known world and the location of Leviathan Sound\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/500px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/750px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/1000px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 42.1%; left: 79.2%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"The known world and the location of Leviathan Sound\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Leviathan Sound\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; top:-0.15em; left: -3em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Leviathan Sound</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a> and the location of Leviathan Sound\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Leviathan Sound</b> is a large bay of the eastern <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a> off the coast of northern <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. It contains a few islands. The <a href=\"/index.php/Howling_Hills\" title=\"Howling Hills\">Howling Hills</a> are to the southwest and the <a href=\"/index.php/Plains_of_the_Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Plains of the Jogos Nhai\">Plains of the Jogos Nhai</a> are to the south.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Leviathan\" title=\"Leviathan\">Leviathans</a> mate and birth their young in Leviathan Sound.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leviathan_Sound&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The Known World.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ic